OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774980702
OL,3,CKing Charles set to visit Trump at the
OL,4,CWhite House
OL,6,FAfter many months of speculation, it's
OL,7,Fbeen confirmed that King Charles will
OL,8,Ftravel to the USA for an official
OL,9,FState Visit, despite the critical
OL,10,Fwords Donald Trump has uttered about
OL,11,Fthe UK's contribution to his conflict
OL,12,Fin Iran.
OL,14,FBuckingham Palace says the visit by
OL,15,Fboth King Charles and Queen Camilla
OL,16,Fwill take place at the end of April
OL,17,Fand will mark the 250th anniversary of
OL,18,FAmerican Independence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
