OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774980702
OL,3,CKing Charles set to visit Trump at the
OL,4,CWhite House
OL,6,FIt will involve a formal State Dinner
OL,7,Fat the White House and a historic
OL,8,Faddress by the British monarch to both
OL,9,Fhouses of Congress in Washington DC.
OL,11,FThe last time that happened was in
OL,12,F1991 when Queen Elizabeth made a
OL,13,Fspeech to Congress during her official
OL,14,Fstate visit.
OL,16,FThe timing of this visit is set
OL,17,Fagainst the backdrop of tensions
OL,18,Fbetween the US president and the
OL,19,FBritish Prime Minister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
