OL,3,CKing Charles set to visit Trump at the
OL,4,CWhite House
OL,6,FForty minutes before the announcement,
OL,7,Fthe US president called on the UK to
OL,8,F"build up some delayed courage" and
OL,9,F"secure" the Strait of Hormuz, the
OL,10,Fessential shipping route that remains
OL,11,Flargely closed due to the war.
OL,13,FTrump previously also criticised Sir
OL,14,FKeir Starmer for being "no Winston
OL,15,FChurchill" and has lashed out at the
OL,16,Flack of resources Britain has sent to
OL,17,Fthe region.
OL,19,FOn his part, Starmer has been clear
OL,20,Fthat this is "not Britain's war and we
OL,21,Fwon't be dragged into it".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774980702
OL,3,CKing Charles set to visit Trump at the
OL,4,CWhite House
OL,6,FIt is a distinct chilling of the Trump-
OL,7,FStarmer relationship since the two
OL,8,Fleaders met in Windsor Castle last
OL,9,Fyear, when Trump was treated to a
OL,10,Fsecond "unprecedented" state visit to
OL,11,Fthe UK.
OL,13,FIt also puts the King in a
OL,14,Fdiplomatically tricky situation
OL,15,Fbecause he is the commander-in-chief
OL,16,Fof the British military, about which
OL,17,FTrump has been so disparaging.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774980702
OL,3,CKing Charles set to visit Trump at the
OL,4,CWhite House
OL,6,FBut British diplomats insist the visit
OL,7,Fis more than about the occupant of the
OL,8,FOval Office at any given time and will
OL,9,Fbe focused on the relationship between
OL,10,Fthe two nations at an important moment
OL,11,Fin American history.
OL,13,FThe US-UK bond is referred to as the
OL,14,F"special relationship", although that
OL,15,Fhas been severely tested during the
OL,16,Fsecond Trump administration, as it has
OL,17,Fbeen among many of America's
OL,18,Ftraditional allies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
