OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774980702
OL,3,CKing Charles set to visit Trump at the
OL,4,CWhite House
OL,6,FITV News understands the King and
OL,7,FQueen will visit New York as well as
OL,8,FWashington DC, but have no plans to
OL,9,Ftravel to the West Coast of the US,
OL,10,Fwhere the King's son, Prince Harry,
OL,11,Flives with his wife Meghan.
OL,13,FKing Charles will make a stop on the
OL,14,Fway home from the US in Bermuda, which
OL,15,Fis a British Overseas Territory.
OL,17,FThe location for state visits by the
OL,18,FBritish monarch is decided by the
OL,19,Fgovernment of the day and reflects the
OL,20,Fprime minister's priorities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774980702
OL,3,CKing Charles set to visit Trump at the
OL,4,CWhite House
OL,6,FKing Charles, therefore, is travelling
OL,7,Fto the US and Bermuda on government
OL,8,Fadvice.
OL,10,FEfforts will be made on both sides of
OL,11,Fthe Atlantic to minimise the risk of
OL,12,FTrump putting the King in a difficult
OL,13,Fdiplomatic position.
OL,15,FBut the truth is, however hard anyone
OL,16,Ftries, no one can predict what the US
OL,17,Fpresident will or won't say during the
OL,18,Fvisit, which is likely to last three
OL,19,Fdays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
